Name: The Revelry that Unveils Mysteries
AttributesDescription:
While Resonators are in mid-air, their DMG dealt is Amplified by 55% for 15s when Resonators are in mid-air.

This Token can be used up to 2 times in Whimpering Wastes.
BgDescription: Sing and dance, my friends! Rejoice in our triumph over a thousand reefs and a thousand storms! Sing and dance, my friends! With gratitude to the Sentinel and memories of our fallen comrades, we shall live proudly on this scorching land!
